OL,3,CShop fined for selling illegal tobacco
OL,4,Cproducts
OL,6,FA company and its former director have
OL,7,Fbeen fined for illegal tobacco and
OL,8,Fnicotine product offences following an
OL,9,Finvestigation by Oxfordshire County
OL,10,FCouncil's trading standards team.
OL,12,FYadgar Ghafour, 38, of Phillip Street,
OL,13,FChester, former owner and director of
OL,14,FKhalifa Super Store Ltd of 120 Cowley
OL,15,FRoad, pleaded guilty to all offences
OL,16,Fat Oxford Magistrates' Court on Friday
OL,17,F28 November and was ordered to pay
OL,18,F#3,907.24 in fines and costs.
