OL,4,Cproducts
OL,6,FThe current owner and director,
OL,7,FMuhemed Hussain, 54, also pleaded
OL,8,Fguilty to all offences on behalf of
OL,9,Fthe company, which must pay #17,616.24
OL,10,Fin fines and costs.
OL,12,FThe court heard that trading standards
OL,13,Fofficers inspected the premises on 1
OL,14,FMay 2024, seizing 160 cigarettes, 35
OL,15,Fpacks of shisha tobacco, 865 vapes and
OL,16,F122 unit packs of nicotine pouches.
OL,17,FThe vapes and shisha were found by a
OL,18,Fdetection dog in compartments sealed
OL,19,Fwith electromagnets, which officers
OL,20,Fhad to force open.
