OL,6,FMost of the nicotine pouches were not
OL,7,Flabelled in English, the tobacco
OL,8,Fproducts were smuggled, and the vapes
OL,9,Fcontained up to nine times the
OL,10,Fpermitted 2ml nicotine liquid capacity.
OL,12,FThe director at the time, Marewan
OL,13,FSalh, 51, of Ridgeway Avenue, Derby
OL,14,Fhas been ordered to pay #2,000 in
OL,15,Ffines and costs at an earlier hearing.
