OL,6,FThe company was then purchased by Mr
OL,7,FGhafour on 26 June 2024, and on 21
OL,8,FJanuary 2025 officers inspected the
OL,9,Fpremises again. They seized 121 unit
OL,10,Fpacks of nicotine pouches that were
OL,11,Feither labelled in a language other
OL,12,Fthan English or that did not have the
OL,13,Frequired safety labelling information.
