OL,6,FFollowing two covert test purchases,
OL,7,Fofficers inspected the premises again
OL,8,Fon 16 March 2025 when a further
OL,9,Fconcealment was discovered built into
OL,10,Fthe shelving units. Inside was 214
OL,11,Fvapes of 10ml capacity and 125 vapes
OL,12,Fof 20ml capacity, 10 times the allowed
OL,13,Flimit.
OL,15,FSmuggled waterpipe tobacco was also
OL,16,Fidentified and seized.
