OL,6,FCouncillor Jenny Hannaby, Oxfordshire
OL,7,FCounty Council's Cabinet Member for
OL,8,FCommunity Safety said: "I am pleased
OL,9,Fthat our trading standards team has
OL,10,Fonce again been able to remove illegal
OL,11,Ftobacco, nicotine pouches and vape
OL,12,Fproducts from our high streets. The
OL,13,Fwork of our officers is vital for
OL,14,Fprotecting residents and holding
OL,15,Findividuals and businesses
OL,16,Faccountable."
